com.vicinityconcepts.lib.cmd

Class TerminalCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vicinityconcepts.lib.cmd.TerminalCommand

  • public class TerminalCommand
extends java.lang.Object
    An object that describes a terminal command including the key used to invoke it, the action it will perform, and other configurations.

    Ryan Palmer
